flowchart TD
    A[Linked GitHub identity on current person] --> B[Load GitHub source candidates]
    B --> C1[Claim evidence browser]
    B --> C2[Contribution import panel]

    C1 --> D1[Import GitHub source into local citation]
    D1 --> E1[Persist citation provenance metadata]
    E1 --> F1[Attach imported citation to evidence link]
    F1 --> G1[Claim uses local bibliography anchor]

    C2 --> D2[Map source kind to role and contribution type]
    D2 --> E2[Find or initialize governed contribution]
    E2 --> F2[Merge source entry into details.github_sources]
    F2 --> G2[Page/Post contribution attribution updated]

    G1 --> H[Bundle and citation exports remain auditable]
    G2 --> H
